            "id": "4521252",
            "title": "Glass House Brands reports Q3 results",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Glass House Brands <a href=\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2025/11/12/3186787/0/en/Glass-House-Brands-Reports-Third-Quarter-2025-Financial-Results.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">press release</a>  (GLASF): Q3 adjusted EBITDA was -$2.3 million, compared to $20.4 million in the third quarter of 2024 and $18.1 million in the second quarter of 2025.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $38.4M (-39.8% Y/Y).</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
