        {
            "id": "4521163",
            "title": "WEBTOON Entertainment stock falls after Q3 miss, forecasts Q4 revenue decline",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">WEBTOON Entertainment (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WBTN\" title=\"WEBTOON Entertainment Inc.\">WBTN</a></span>) dropped <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">24%</span> in premarket trading on Thursday after the company forecast a revenue decline in the range of 5.1%-2.3% in the fourth quarter, following a Q3 miss.</p>\n<p>Adjusted EBITDA loss is also expected in the range of $6.5-$1.5 million.</p>\n<p>Management cited \"pressure from IP adaptations related to the timing of milestones\" and ongoing infrastructure updates as factors in the Q4 guidance.</p>\n<p>The adjusted EBITDA outlook includes $16.5 million in noncash expenses, including actuarial losses on retiree benefits and minimum guarantee write-downs.</p>\n<p>When inquired about the Warner Bros. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WBD\" title=\"Warner Bros. Discovery, Inc.\">WBD</a>) partnership timing and economics and about trends in Wattpad and web novel MAU, CFO David Lee described the Warner Bros. deal as a catalyst for growth but said \"we are not really in a position to offer more specifics\" at this time. </p>\n<p>Lee also said it is \"too early\" to give specific quantified metrics for Disney (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DIS\" title=\"The Walt Disney Company\">DIS</a>) engagement but is \"very encouraged by the progress we're making\" in North America. </p>\n<p>YTD, the stock is up 24%. </p>\n<p> </p>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4521163-webtoon-entertainment-stock-falls-after-q3-miss-forecasts-q4-revenue-decline",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-13 18:15:44",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
